WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:04.696
Today, I want to tell you
about a pressing social issue.

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:07.056
Now, it's not nuclear arms,

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:08.656
it's not immigration,

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:10.616
and it's not malaria.

00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:14.096
I'm here to talk about movies.

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:17.680
Now, in all seriousness,
movies are actually really important.

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:22.656
In film, we can be wildly entertained,

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:27.000
and we can also be transported
through storytelling.

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:29.296
Storytelling is so important.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:32.856
Stories tell us what societies value,